properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 25 at 5:11AM AKST until January 26 at 5:00AM AKST by NWS Juneau AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow expected. Total snow accumulations of 3 to 5 inches.

* WHERE...Juneau Borough and Northern Admiralty Island.

* WHEN...From 6 PM this evening to 5 AM AKST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. Heavy wet snow will
be difficult to manage. The morning commute will be adversely
impacted.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 6 PM THIS EVENING TO 5 AM AKST SUNDAY
